# Jumping Game – Java 2D Platformer

A fast-paced 2D jumping game built in Java using Swing. Features smooth player movement, jump mechanics, collision detection, state-based animations, and score tracking. Demonstrates OOP principles, game loop logic, and event-driven programming.

---

## Key Features

- Player movement: Run, Jump, Roll
- Collision detection with obstacles
- Game state management (running, jumping, rolling)
- Score tracking system
- Smooth animations and responsive controls

---

## Technologies Used

- Java
- Swing
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)
- Event-driven programming

---